reviewText: My son is very happy with the DVD great purchase.
I like it but the grandson loves it!
Disc was slightly scratched and skips in the beginning of the video. I knew it was used but should of stated that it could possibly not work properly.

This DVD contains six episodes from the Wow! Wow! Wubbzy! cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Once Upon A Wubbzy
2. The Big Birthday Mystery
3. Welcome To The Dollhouse
4. Happily Ever After
5. Too Many Wubbzys
6. Focus Wubbzy

The most important factor when ordering a DVD like this is if my 4 granddaughters will like it.  Well, they did like it so grandpa did good.  I did watch it with them and as with all Wuzzby shows I have seen of TV, he manages to get into trouble and still comes out a winner.  I am pleased with the purchase even though my mind is over 7 decades older that my oldest granddaughter.
